{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_10_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 私と一緒に恋の炎に包まれよう！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――探訪番組ロケの三時間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Three Hours Before the Location Show Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュールを調整していただいて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for adjusting the schedule.\nI really appreciate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ロケの開始時間を後ろ倒しに出来て良かったよ\n本当は前日とかにしたかったんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s good we could push back the start time of the shoot.\nI wanted to do it the day before‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、むしろ直前の方が下見の経験を\nすぐに本番に活かせますから問題ありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ actually doing it just before allows me to\nimmediately apply the experience to the real shoot‚ so it’s no problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.3999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あらかじめ料理や地理は把握していますが\nやはり実際に歩くのとは勝手が違いますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already know the food and geography in advance‚\nbut it’s not the same as actually walking around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まずはどこから行きたい？\n沙季の好きな所からでいいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where do you want to start?\nLet’s start wherever you like‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "では、まずは神社に行きましょうか\nこの町で最も由緒ある場所らしいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ shall we start with the shrine?\nIt seems to be the most historic place in this town.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "何事もまずは雰囲気から、と言いますからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say that the atmosphere comes first for everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6333331704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――神社",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Shrine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3333331704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "この神社は創建されてから千年以上の年月が\n経過しているらしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This shrine has been around for over a thousand years\nsince its founding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛成就の神様が祀られていることから\n沢山の人でいつも賑わっているそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the god of fulfilled love is enshrined here‚\nit’s always bustling with many people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.6666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "凄く詳しいな\nまるで本物のガイドさんみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re very knowledgeable‚\nlike a real tour guide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "事前にロケ地の勉強をしてきましたから\n案内をするぐらいであれば問題ありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I studied the location in advance‚\nso I can guide people without any problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.0999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、恋愛についての勉強もしてきましたよ\n今回の鬼門はそこでしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I also studied about romance‚\nbecause that was the tricky part this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.299598095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちなみに、どんなことを勉強してきたのか\n一応聞かせてもらってもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…By the way‚ just in case‚ could you tell me\nwhat exactly you studied?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3565605998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "これは渚ちゃんから借りた少女漫画に\n載っていたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was in a girls manga\nI borrowed from Nagisa-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも、人は相手から「おもしれーやつ」と\n言われると心がときめいてしまうらしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ when someone is called “interesting”\nby the other person‚ their heart starts to flutter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、壁に追いやられた状態であごを掴まれたら\nドキドキしてしまうとも書かれていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ it said that if someone is cornered against a wall and\ntheir chin is grabbed‚ their heart will race as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "これは壁ドンと呼ばれているらしいです\n行為に対して名前が少々物騒ですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is apparently called a “wall slam.”\nThe name for the act sounds a bit alarming‚ doesn’t it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.5333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、恋愛とはどれだけ相手を翻弄出来るかに\nかかっていると言っても過言ではないということです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ it’s not an exaggeration to say that love\ndepends on how much you can toy with the other person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛においてシチュエーションが大事だとは\nよく言うから、あながち間違ってもいないのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They often say that situations are important in romance‚\nso maybe it’s not entirely wrong…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "少女漫画の他にも、平安時代あたりの恋についても\n勉強してきたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides girls manga‚ I also studied romance\nfrom the Heian period…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、百人一首の五十二番にて\n藤原道信はこんな和歌を詠んでいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ in the 52nd poem of the Hyakunin Isshu‚\nFujiwara no Michinobu wrote:",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "「明けぬれば暮るるものとは知りながら\nなほ恨めしき朝ぼらけかな」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Though I know that night will come again after the day has dawned‚\nI still resent the breaking of the morning.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "これは、恋人と別れなければならない夜明けなんて\n嫌いだ、という意味の和歌なのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This poem expresses the dislike of dawn\nwhen one must part from their lover…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1613918208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "翌日も会えるはずなのに残念だなぁなどと思って\nしまうのは、どうしてだろうと考えてしまいまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though they are supposed to see each other the next day‚\nI find myself wondering why it still feels so sad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
